<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Weblog - tomazursic.github.io - git</title><link href="/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="/feeds/git.tag.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>/</id><updated>2017-07-08T00:00:00+02:00</updated><entry><title>Git Notes</title><link href="/git.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2017-07-08T00:00:00+02:00</published><updated>2017-07-08T00:00:00+02:00</updated><author><name>Tomaz</name></author><id>tag:None,2017-07-08:/git.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p class="first last"&gt;Notes using git&lt;/p&gt;
</summary><content type="html">&lt;div class="section" id="git-tips"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Git Tips&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="section" id="reset"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Reset&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reset current git repo to match remote&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Save&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;work&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;co&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;save&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;work&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;co&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;master&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;fetch&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;origin&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;reset&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;--hard origin/master&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remove wrong commit from master.
Reset reassign the branch pointer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;HEAD&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class="n"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;commit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;currently&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;siting&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="o"&gt;^&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;HEAD&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="n"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;commit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;parent&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="o"&gt;^^&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;HEAD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;commit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;grandparent&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;co&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;master&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;reset&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;--hard ^HEAD&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reset last commit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;reset&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;--hard HEAD~1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="section" id="contribute"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Contribute&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make Fork on webpage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create local clone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add remote upstrem to original repo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;$ git remote add upstream https://github.com/octocat/Spoon-Knife.git
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple" start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;View remote&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;$ git remote -v
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple" start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sync a fork&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;$ git fetch upstream
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple" start="6"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Branch set to track upsream master&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;$ git branch --set-upstream-to&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;upstream/master master
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple" start="7"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create new brnch for working on&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;$ git checkout -b &amp;lt;branch-name&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple" start="8"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create changes, commit and push to origin remote&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;$ git push -u origin &amp;lt;branch-name&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple" start="9"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create Pull Request in GUI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</content><category term="notes"></category><category term="git"></category><category term="linux"></category></entry></feed>